                     <note type="general">Actual dimensions of item are 23.5 x 15.0 cm</note>
                     <note type="general">26 lines</note>
                     <note type="general">Written across the fibers on the recto in an unpractised hand</note>
                     <note type="general">Small lower margin; left margin of 1 cm.; small right margin</note>
                     <note type="general">P.Duk.inv. 460 was formerly P.Miss. 26</note>
